The Cricket Club and Golf Club are both on Whitchurch Down. The {Golf}Club has 700 playing members and 500 social members.The course is 6250 yards long and has 120 bunkers.The club was founded in 1890.The club also has a golf professional who gives lessons. Children from 9 years old can join.The club has a restaurant and a bar, and holds many social functions.
{* * * * * * * * * * *}
The {Cricket }Club is only open from May to the third week in September.It was founded in 1849.About 10 teams play from First Eleven to Under 11's. The boundary is marked by granite stones.
